snippet.title: Belt Miners - Trailer #4
snippet.description:
Advertisement video for Belt Miners v2.0:
http://beltminers.com

Belt Miners is a sci-fi asteroid mining simulation game that is made for the Oculus Gear VR and Google Daydream VR devices.

We hope you click Subscribe, to stay tuned..

Thanks to Stellardrone for creating the music (CC BY 3.0):
http://stellardrone.bandcamp.com
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
